  weight,

###diagnostic plots

#task

model <- lm(y ~ x,
            data = distr_1)
autoplot(model)

distr_1 %>% 
  add_predictions(model) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = x))+
  geom_point(aes(y = y))+
  geom_line(aes(y = pred), col = "red")

linear model doesn’t fit data , there is a curvature of the plot
